### CRM - Messages
### Email communication with contacts

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@merchantToken = YOUR_MERCHANT_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@contactId = YOUR_CONTACT_ID_HERE

### Send email reply to contact
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/messages/send
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactId": "{{contactId}}",
  "body": "Thank you for reaching out! We're excited to discuss how our services can help your business grow. When would be a good time for a call?"
}

### Send follow-up email
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/messages/send
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactId": "{{contactId}}",
  "body": "Hi there! Just following up on my previous email. Have you had a chance to review our proposal?"
}

### Get all messages for a contact
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/messages/contact/{{contactId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Get messages filtered by direction - outgoing only
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/messages/contact/{{contactId}}?direction=outgoing
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Get messages filtered by direction - incoming only
GET {{baseUrl}}/crm/messages/contact/{{contactId}}?direction=incoming
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}

### Error - Send to non-existent contact (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/messages/send
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactId": "000000000000000000000000",
  "body": "This will fail because contact doesn't exist"
}

### Error - Empty message body (should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/crm/messages/send
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactId": "{{contactId}}",
  "body": ""
}
